    "body": "Dynamic cut of the long names happens right now, yes. However, we cut username too soon. So there is a large gap stays on any screen width:\r\nFor instance Android on 4.5” screen:\r\nPopular hashtag/Recent statuses view:\r\n![popular_4_5](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/34204308-cc21caf6-e586-11e7-910b-9232b376e5c8.png)\r\n\r\nPopular hashtag/Recent statuses -> ‘All’ view:\r\n![popular_all_4_5](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/34204315-d18e2c1e-e586-11e7-8171-f9662c0802cf.png)\r\n\r\nAndroid on 5.5” screen\r\nPopular hashtag/Recent statuses view:\r\n![popular_5_5](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/34204327-dbf1ec18-e586-11e7-86d9-97d2f05b2c1d.png)\r\n\r\nPopular hashtag/Recent statuses -> ‘All’ view:\r\n![popular_all_5_5](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/34204333-e1cce692-e586-11e7-8e4f-d0d3c2782476.png)\r\n\r\niOS screens:\r\nDiscover view with no Chat button:\r\n![iosdiscover](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/34204609-f5882754-e587-11e7-8ece-5eed5c11117c.png)\r\n\r\nPopular hashtag -> ALL, iOS view:\r\n![popular_all_ios](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/34204625-05c4f7be-e588-11e7-8769-cfc47f20c3e4.png)\r\n\r\nRecent hashtag -> ALL, iOS view:\r\n![recent_all_ios](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/34204637-1867075e-e588-11e7-8bde-cca7d2155559.png)\r\n\r\n@foopang Could you increase, please, the number of chars we display before cut username off?\r\nAlso, lets do the same for usernames on cards without Chat button (users own cards - see iOS screen above)\r\n\r\nImplementation may look similar to this: \r\nCalculate the available space for username before chat button (if there is no Chat button then take a width of the card). Calculate width of username, - if username length exceed the available space -> cut username and prolong with three dots.",
